search_results.title: Justin Oakley
search_results.snippet: Justin Oakley is a bioethicist and moral philosopher. He has been part of the revival of the ethical doctrine known as virtue ethics.

search_results.title: Justin Oakley
search_results.snippet: Professor Justin Oakley BA, PhD (Philosophy) is Deputy Director of Monash Bioethics Centre, at Monash University. He is the author of Morality and the Emotions.
